    "description": "<strong>&quot;揭开坠落泪珠重返地面之旅的神秘面纱！&quot;</strong><br><br><i>Tears Fall Low</i> 是一款令人着迷的 2D 平台游戏，充满了创新机制和具有挑战性的游戏玩法。在攀爬出黑暗洞穴走向地表的过程中，探索丰富多样的世界！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380130/extras/5fa76c1c0882da6a59c8d134c7ab169c.poster.avif?t=1685833591\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380130/extras/5fa76c1c0882da6a59c8d134c7ab169c.webm?t=1685833591\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380130/extras/5fa76c1c0882da6a59c8d134c7ab169c.mp4?t=1685833591\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>作为一颗坠落的泪珠，开始穿越地球深处隐藏的深渊的旅程，克服可怕的危险。每个区域都有自己的秘密和危险，呈现出独特的障碍和挑战，测试你的技巧和智慧。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380130/extras/4bb0ca71538114819eaea61dc14f8f54.poster.avif?t=1685833591\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380130/extras/4bb0ca71538114819eaea61dc14f8f54.webm?t=1685833591\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380130/extras/4bb0ca71538114819eaea61dc14f8f54.mp4?t=1685833591\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在游戏过程中解锁你的真正潜力，变得越来越强大，以面对地下的强大怪物。深入探索一个引人入胜的故事，以意想不到和奇特的方式展开......<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380130/extras/98289f7d4f6ed0ba2ae60650e9493016.poster.avif?t=1685833591\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380130/extras/98289f7d4f6ed0ba2ae60650e9493016.webm?t=1685833591\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380130/extras/98289f7d4f6ed0ba2ae60650e9493016.mp4?t=1685833591\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>神秘且引人入胜的世界<br></li><li>具有挑战性的平台跳跃<br></li><li>充满吸引力的主题的引人入胜的故事</li></ul>",
